> Which is, in turn, is caused by this code:
> 
> --- linux-2.6.17.6.org/sound/core/pcm_compat.c	2006-07-15 21:00:43.000000000 +0200
> +++ linux-2.6.17.6.src/sound/core/pcm_compat.c	2006-07-28 00:35:10.000000000 +0200
